eight: autopx;\"\u003e200MP + 50MP + 10MP + 12MP Quad Rear Camera\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e200 MP, f\/1.7, 24mm (wide), 1\/1.3\", 0.6µm, multi-directional PDAF, Laser AF, OIS\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e50 MP, f\/3.4, 111mm (periscope telephoto), PDAF, OIS, 5x optical zoom\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e10 MP, f\/2.4, 67mm (telephoto), 1\/3.52\", 1.12µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, OIS, 3x optical zoom\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e12 MP, f\/2.2, 13mm, 120˚ (ultrawide), 1\/2.55\", 1.4µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, Super Steady video\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003eFront Camera\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e12MP Front Camera\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003e12 MP, f\/2.2, 26mm (wide), Dual Pixel PDAF\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: autopx;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003eCamera Features\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: auto%; height: autopx;\"\u003eLED flash, auto-HDR, panorama, Dual video call\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u00