  "description": "\n\n\nModel\nSamsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G \n\n\nDisplay Size\n6.8 inches Display\n\n\nDisplay Type\nDynamic LTPO AMOLED 2X, 120Hz, HDR10+, 2600 nits (peak), Quad HD+ | 1440 x 3088 pixels (501 ppi)\n\n\nOS\nAndroid 14, One UI 6.1\n\n\nChipset\nQualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 (4 nm)\n\n\nCPU\nOcta-core (1x3.3 GHz Cortex-X4 \u0026amp; 5x3.2 GHz Cortex-A720 \u0026amp; 2x2.3 GHz Cortex-A520)\n\n\nGPU\nAdreno 750\n\n\nRAM \u0026amp; ROM\n12GB RAM | 256GB ROM\n\n\nRear Camera\n200MP Quad Rear Camera\n\n\n\n200MP + 50MP + 10MP + 12MP Quad Rear Camera\n\n\n\n200 MP, f\/1.7, 24mm (wide), 1\/1.3\", 0.6µm, multi-directional PDAF, Laser AF, OIS\n\n\n\n50 MP, f\/3.4, 111mm (periscope telephoto), PDAF, OIS, 5x optical zoom\n\n\n\n10 MP, f\/2.4, 67mm (telephoto), 1\/3.52\", 1.12µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, OIS, 3x optical zoom\n\n\n\n12 MP, f\/2.2, 13mm, 120˚ (ultrawide), 1\/2.55\", 1.4µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, Super Steady video\n\n\nFront Camera\n12MP Front Camera\n\n\n\n12 MP, f\/2.2, 26mm (wide), Dual Pixel PDAF\n\n\nCamera Features\nLED flash, auto-HDR, panorama, Dual video call\n\n\nAudio\nStereo Speakers\n\n\n\n32-bit\/384kHz audio | Tuned by AKG\n\n\nVideo\n8K@24\/30fps, 4K@30\/60\/120fps, 1080p@30\/60\/240fps, 1080p@960fps, HDR10+, stereo sound rec., gyro-EIS\n\n\nNetwork\n2G bands – GSM  850 \/ 900 \/ 1800 \/ 1900 - SIM 1 \u0026amp; SIM 2\n\n\n\n3G bands - HSDPA 850 \/ 900 \/ 1700(AWS) \/ 1900 \/ 2100\n\n\n\n4G bands - 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 8, 12, 17, 20, 26, 28, 32, 38, 40, 41, 66\n\n\n\n5G bands - 1, 3, 7, 8, 20, 28, 38, 40, 41, 77, 78 SA\/NSA\/Sub6\n\n\nBluetooth\n5.3, A2DP, LE,\n\n\nUSB\nUSB Type-C 3.2, OTG\n\n\nWLAN\nWi-Fi 802.11 a\/b\/g\/n\/ac\/6e, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct\n\n\nNFC\nYes\n\n\nSensor\nFingerprint (under-display, optical) | accelerometer | gyro | Proximity | Compass | Barometer\n\n\nBattery Capacity\nLi-Ion 5000mAh, non-removable\n\n\n\n45W wired, PD3.0, 65% in 30 min (adverticed)\n\n\n\n15W Wireless\n\n\n\n4.5W Reverse Wireless\n\n\nDimension\n162.3 x 79 x